strategies for doing the load balalncing
1. Round robin
2. Least connections
3. Consistent hashing

Few solutions
nginx
HAproxy
AWS elastic load balancer

advantages
1. scaling beocomes easy as we can add pr remove the server
2. reliability - can find unhealthy server and replace them 
3. Performance - by distributing load evenly load balancer can provide reduced response time

disadvantages
1. there should be multiple load balancers to avoid single point of failure
2 deployment will take longer as it will need to redirect to new servers
